@startuml
title Bridge - Estrutura

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Client

abstract class Abstraction {
  - implementor: Implementor
  + operation(): void
}

class RefinedAbstractionA {
  + operation(): void
}

class RefinedAbstractionB {
  + operation(): void
}

interface Implementor {
  + implementationOperation(): void
}

class ConcreteImplementorA {
  + implementationOperation(): void
}

class ConcreteImplementorB {
  + implementationOperation(): void
}

Client --> Abstraction : usa
Abstraction *-- Implementor : delega
RefinedAbstractionA --|> Abstraction
RefinedAbstractionB --|> Abstraction
ConcreteImplementorA ..|> Implementor
ConcreteImplementorB ..|> Implementor

note right of Abstraction
  A abstração e a implementação
  variam em hierarquias independentes.
end note

@enduml

@startuml
title Bridge - Comunicação

actor Client
participant RefinedAbstraction
participant ConcreteImplementor

Client -> RefinedAbstraction : operation()
RefinedAbstraction -> RefinedAbstraction : aplica regra de negócio
RefinedAbstraction -> ConcreteImplementor : implementationOperation()
ConcreteImplementor --> RefinedAbstraction : resultado técnico
RefinedAbstraction --> Client : resultado final

@enduml
